title: Brett Kavanaugh - Unlocked Premium Episode
itunes:title: Brett Kavanaugh - Unlocked Premium Episode
description:
The hosts pound some brewskis with Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh.


Normally there would be no episode in the free feed this week, but we decided to do something special for ya. This episode was originally exclusively available to our Patreon members, but we're giving you a peek into the premium feed. If you enjoyed the episode and want to unlock more like it, like our just-released episode about Originalism, join our Patreon at $5 a month, at patreon.com/fivefourpod.


Follow Peter (@The_Law_Boy), Rhiannon (@AywaRhiannon) and Michael (@_FleerUltra) on Twitter.


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
